```

### View Tracking History

```bash
# View recent history
phonetracker history

# View history for specific number
phonetracker history +254712345678

# Limit number of records
phonetracker history --limit 20

# Export to CSV
phonetracker history --export csv --output ./tracks.csv

# Export to JSON
phonetracker history --export json --output ./tracks.json
```

### Configuration Management

```bash
# Show current configuration
phonetracker config --show

# Set configuration values
phonetracker config --set voip.account_sid=ACxxx
phonetracker config --set voip.auth_token=xxx
phonetracker config --set voip.phone_number=+1xxx
phonetracker config --set location.method=basic
phonetracker config --set auth.require_confirmation=true
phonetracker config --set display.show_map_link=true

# Reset to defaults
phonetracker config --reset
```

### View Audit Logs

```bash
# View authorization logs
phonetracker logs

# Limit log entries
phonetracker logs --limit 100
```

### Clear History

```bash
# Clear history for specific number
phonetracker clear --phone +254712345678

# Clear all history
phonetracker clear --all
```

### System Information

```bash
phonetracker info
```

## âš™ï¸ Configuration

Configuration is stored at `~/.phonetracker/config.yaml`:

```yaml
voip:
  provider: twilio
  account_sid: ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
  auth_token: your_auth_token_here
  phone_number: +1234567890

location:
  method: basic          # basic, carrier, or gps
  fallback: true
  carrier_api_key: ''    # Required for carrier method

auth:
  require_confirmation: true
  log_all_requests: true
  allowed_users: []

display:
  show_map_link: true
  color_output: true
  verbose: false
  ascii_map: false

database:
  encrypt: false
  path: ~/.phonetracker/history.db

rate_limit:
  max_per_hour: 10
  max_per_day: 50
```

## ğŸ” Location Methods

### Basic (Default)
- Uses phone number prefix database
- Provides country/city level accuracy (~5km)
- No external API required
- Fastest method

### Carrier (Advanced)
- Uses carrier API for cell tower triangulation
- Provides better accuracy (~500m)
- Requires carrier API credentials
- Not yet implemented (placeholder)

### GPS (Requires Device Cooperation)
- Highest accuracy (~10m)
- Requires app on target device
- Not yet implemented (placeholder)

